close_reason: "Published a typed SDK output-ownership protocol, integrated CLI suppression, and proved single-write stdout with a packed package."
body: "GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/547\n\nThis is backlog tracking only in the current immutable-history/read implementation lane. Reuse the public output contracts and avoid package-specific sentinels."
